snippet.title: Herta and Friends's Epic Swing on Swing Rhythm! (Lyrics) / KuruKuru Song Full Ver. Piano / Star Rail
snippet.description:
Honkai: Star rail - Herta Japanese CV Edit Song Piano Performance


* This work is a submission for the 2023 Honkai: Star Rail creator competition

The original Japanese combat voice can be heard here. 
(https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AAKsX-uqinU)


KuruKuru~ Kururin~ Epic Swing on Swing Rhythm!

Today is Herta's "Kurukuru Kururin" theme that many people have been waiting for.
Thanks to Bailu's response, "I'm a borrowed barley sack," I tried again!

Originally I was going to play a simple version of an existing meme, but
I made a full version of a song because I wanted to work hard on what I have always wanted to do.

Since the existing memes were in Japanese, I used Japanese voice lines for natural production.
If you do not use Japanese voices, please refer to the subtitles.

And thanks to the creators who provided good sources
I was a little greedy and added a few parts.

In addition to Herta, they are the friends that come to mind when I think of round and round~~
Check out the video to find out who the main characters are!!

Thank you for listening.

---------------------------------------------------
Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/Frostmusic
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
---------------------------------------------------
Bailu's Song "Hymn to the Barley Sack" (Subtitled) : https://youtu.be/1KB__dvffgo
"Wildfire(野火)" Cocoria Battle Ver. Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/QoMyufVFqcI
「Honkai: Star rail」 Login(Main) Theme 「Star Rail」 Piano : https://youtu.be/bTNo65uX3SM
Honkai: Star rail - Global Tour 「Seoul: COEX」 (Subtilted) : https://youtu.be/ftpGE9NSwbI
"Star Rail" busking on the street : https://youtu.be/2XNqxmlW4Cg
---------------------------------------------------
템플릿 : 론박자막연구소
Source : https://www.youtube.com/@dr.taskdesk, https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zUcmK4xsllA
Piano Sheet : Updating..
---------------------------------------------------
